import React, { useState } from "react";
import {
  MDBBtn,
  MDBModal,
  MDBModalDialog,
  MDBModalContent,
  MDBModalHeader,
  MDBModalTitle,
  MDBModalBody,
  MDBModalFooter,
} from "mdb-react-ui-kit";
import TransactionForm from "./TransactionForm";

export default function PartnersModal() {
  const [basicModal, setBasicModal] = useState(false);

  const toggleShow = () => setBasicModal(!basicModal);

  return (
    <>
      <MDBBtn
        outline
        className="float-end"
        color="success"
        onClick={toggleShow}
      >
        Transaktion hinzufügen
      </MDBBtn>
      <MDBModal show={basicModal} setShow={setBasicModal} tabIndex="-1">
        <MDBModalDialog>
          <MDBModalContent>
            <MDBModalHeader>
              <MDBModalTitle>Transaktionen hinzufügen</MDBModalTitle>
              <MDBBtn
                className="btn-close"
                color="none"
                onClick={toggleShow}
              ></MDBBtn>
            </MDBModalHeader>
            <MDBModalBody>
              <TransactionForm />
            </MDBModalBody>
            <MDBModalFooter>
              <MDBBtn color="danger" onClick={toggleShow}>
                Abbrechen
              </MDBBtn>
            </MDBModalFooter>
          </MDBModalContent>
        </MDBModalDialog>
      </MDBModal>
    </>
  );
}
